WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.000
So once I do that, you can see this session is starting.

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:07.000
And one of the other advantages of Posit Workbench is if I want to start

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:10.000
another session at the exact same time, I can do that.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:13.000
I can have more than one VS Code session going.

00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:15.000
I can have an RStudio session going.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:20.000
I can have a Jupyter... we'll open a Jupyter Notebook session going.

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:23.000
And this is a great way if you're working on multiple projects

00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:25.000
using different languages and different IDEs,

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:27.000
you can have them all going simultaneously

00:00:27.000 --> 00:00:31.000
and easily switch between the four that I've created here.

